title: Georgia Bulldogs vs. Clemson Tigers | Full Game Highlights
author: ESPN College Football
description:
Georgia Bulldogs vs. Clemson Tigers | Full Game Highlights

The No. 5 Georgia Bulldogs beat the No. 3 Clemson Tigers, 10-3, in the Duke’s Mayo Classic to kick off the 2021 college football season. The lone TD of the game was scored by Georgia DB Christopher Smith on a pick-6 of Clemson QB D.J. Uiagalelei.
